    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation level for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at Gradation 1. The single operating point yielding RHI = 1.04 was reviewed against the hemolytic performance acceptability requirement and judged to represent minimal additional hemolytic burden relative to the predicate, consistent with acceptable hemolytic performance as defined in the governing requirement. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the defined COU.",
